This paper deals with the analysis of the degree of freedom (DoF) region and sum DoF for multi-hop relay wireless networks, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and networking (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the capacity limitations of multi-hop networks, which can be considered as a system control problem (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper deals with the optimization of scheduling and routing, which is a topic related to multimedia (cs.MM) and computer engineering (cs.CE).
